    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/532b72f9a99c449544c9a317c4a879c0.poster.avif?t=1771967356\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/532b72f9a99c449544c9a317c4a879c0.webm?t=1771967356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/532b72f9a99c449544c9a317c4a879c0.mp4?t=1771967356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在宁静的北方岛屿上出现了外来的威胁。居住在此的菲约尔尚未足够强大，但她生于守护者的天赐祝福之下，必须激发内在力量，联合古代英雄的灵魂，履行保护自己民族神圣事物的使命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存、变强并取得胜利。在追求目标的过程中，探索岛屿的地表和地下：被遗忘的洞穴、阴森的沼泽、幽暗的地下墓穴和神圣的废墟，在这些地方，你将与成群的怪物战斗，并发现精心隐藏的秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>高级战斗系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/fb17ee810defbeb896c4d8f4e9dac019.poster.avif?t=1771967356\" width=1170 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/fb17ee810defbeb896c4d8f4e9dac019.webm?t=1771967356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/fb17ee810defbeb896c4d8f4e9dac019.mp4?t=1771967356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厌倦了单一按钮的战斗？受最佳砍杀类游戏的启发，Divinum 为你提供广泛的探索和掌握空间。将敌人击飞至空中，使他们无力反击，同时菲约尔可施展独特招式。使用两种截然不同的主要武器和特殊技能，进行连贯的连击。通过迅捷的闪避、格挡和反击不给敌人任何机会！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>显著的装备增益</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/5e9af5b1262ba12540400afd50771682.poster.avif?t=1771967356\" width=614 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/5e9af5b1262ba12540400afd50771682.webm?t=1771967356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/5e9af5b1262ba12540400afd50771682.mp4?t=1771967356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索世界、寻找秘密并挑战首领，获取可以极大改变战斗风格的符文。+5% 的伤害加成？在 Divinum 中你不会遇到如此无趣的物品。符文提供独特的增益效果，甚至包括完全改变玩家战斗方式的效果。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>考验你的技能并赢取奖励</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/426c5f5fea36bbf425fb3b83a4c87410.poster.avif?t=1771967356\" width=1170 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/426c5f5fea36bbf425fb3b83a4c87410.webm?t=1771967356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1148130/extras/426c5f5fea36bbf425fb3b83a4c87410.mp4?t=1771967356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整个岛屿上，古老的邪恶势力潜伏待机。向诅咒的古敌发起挑战，并获得应得的奖励。</p>",
